data.description: Pride of ownership shows throughout this beautifully kept home. This home features 4 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms with an oversized 1 car garage, and has been beautifully remodeled with brand new flooring, paint and bathroom vanities in both bathrooms. Basement has 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom with a large separate living area and still plenty of storage in the utility room. Backyard has a privacy fence, covered patio and is a great place to entertain. Call now to see this move in ready home!
